	AND INFO HERE</u></a> TIMING: 4pm doors <br><br><br><br>ALL AGES (under 21
	 will be restricted to the fest stage area after 8pm)<br><br>2 stages (The
	 Attic &amp\; Fest Stage) | 4pm doors | $16 presale $18 DOS<br><br>This mi
	xed genre showcase takes over Axelrad for a full night of live music featu
	ring 20 bands from across Texas. Blending shoegaze\, indie\, emo\, alterna
	tive\, electronic\, and everything in between\, the lineup is built to sho
	wcase the variety and creativity of the Texas DIY scene all in one place.<
