UID:FgHVipoGGrNqruI0vJntL
SUMMARY:Father's Day Ol' Smokey Competition
DTSTAMP:20260618T030750Z
DTSTART:20260620T120000Z
DESCRIPTION:DADS\, THIS ONE’S FOR YOU!\nJoin us for Dadapalooza from 1–5 PM
	 at the brewery\, an afternoon dedicated to all things Dad. We’ll have cur
	ated local vendors on-site selling dad goods\, cold beer flowing\, and ple
	nty of questionable dad jokes.\nStarting at 2 PM\, dads will go head-to-he
	ad in a series of elite competitions including:\n-Burger Flipping Flair Co
	ntest\n– Best Dad Fit Competition\n– LEGO Walk\n– Speed Diaper Changing Ch
	allenge\nCompete for your chance to win awesome prizes including an Ol’ Sm
	okey Grill\, a Cutthroat Barbers gift card\, a Eureka Heights gift card\, 
	and of course… beer.\nBring your dad\, your baby daddy\, your grandpa\, yo
	ur grill master\, or just your best pair of white New Balances. See y’all 
	there.\n\nhttps://www.eurekaheights.com/event/fathers-day-ol-smokey-compet
	ition-2026-06-20/\n\nFrom Eureka Heights Brewery
