SUMMARY:Moonlight Movie Nights: Lilo & Stitch
DTSTAMP:20260618T030750Z
DTSTART:20260627T203000Z
DESCRIPTION:As part of this summer’s Kicking It at Hermann Park offerings\,
	 enjoy “Moonlight Movie Nights\,” presented by Goya\, in the Commons! On S
	aturday\, June 27\, join us for a showing of Lilo & Stitch (2002 | PG | 1h
	 25m runtime). \nThe movie will start at approximately 8:30 p.m.\, around 
	sunset. The movie showing is free and open to the public. \nBe sure to get
	 to the Commons early to snag your spot on the lawn. Guests are welcome to
	 bring blankets or lawn chairs to settle in for the movie. \nFood and beve
	rage will be available for purchase at the cafe and with food vendors on-s
	ite. \nThank you to Goya for their generous support!\n\nhttps://hermannpar
	k.org/event/moonlight-movie-nights-lilo-stitch/\n\nFrom Hermann Park Conse
	rvancy
