SUMMARY:Bubbles and Fireworks Boat Tour
DTSTAMP:20260618T030750Z
DTSTART:20260704T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Hop aboard BBP’s pontoon boat for perfect views of Houston’s sp
	ectacular fireworks show! \nAvoid the crowds and view the city’s fireworks
	 extravaganza while floating along Buffalo Bayou and enjoying bubbly\, bee
	r\, wine and light bites. We can only accommodate 21 lucky guests\, so reg
	ister now! \nBoat tours leave from Allen’s Landing (1005 Commerce Street).
	 \nCost: $150 per person \nNote: Children under the age of 4 are not allow
	ed on the pontoon boat. \nPURCHASE TICKETS\n\nhttps://buffalobayou.org/eve
	nt/2026-bubbles-and-fireworks-boat-tour/\n\nFrom Buffalo Bayou Partnership
URL:https://buffalobayou.org/event/2026-bubbles-and-fireworks-boat-tour/
LOCATION:ALLEN’S LANDING\, 1001 Commerce Street\, Houston\, TX\, 77002\, Un
	ited States
